# Internal design docs / audits / handoffs — kept locally for development
# reference but not part of the public repo. The README in the repo root
# is the public-facing project description; everything under docs/ is
# implementation history, design rationale, and migration notes.
docs/

# Internal meta / agent + planning docs — kept locally, not part of the public
# repo (also removed from history during the open-source cleanup).
/CLAUDE.md
/CONTEXT-MAP.md
**/CONTEXT.md
/android/IMPLEMENTATION-PLAN.md

# Defensive env-file pattern — covers any future subdirectory that might
# carry secrets. The web/ shell already excludes `.env.local` via its own
# .gitignore; this root entry catches strays from new sub-projects.
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Local DE1/BLE traffic captures — large JSONL replays, dev artefact only.
captures/
